data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the sought-after Raindance neighborhood! This spacious ranch home with finished basement offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and entertainment. Home features 6 bedroom, 5 bathrooms, office, and rec room. The open floor-plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The heart of the home is the stunning kitchen featuring double ovens, gas cooking top, quartz countertops, and generous island. The finished basement provides added rec and entertainment space that includes a wet-bar. Enjoy the backyard with mountain views, natural gas firepit, that backs to the walking/golf cart trail.
